title: Grand Hotel Dore
description:
The Grand Hôtel Doré is a charming traditional 3-star hotel in the area of Daumesnil in the 12th arrondissement. After renovation work, the hotel now features a warm setting, combining modern design and traditional charm. The rooms are cozy and well equipped. Each room is decorated following a unique theme. Sober colors such as beige and white meet with flaming red and orange for a quiet and peaceful atmosphere.
The hotel is located near the business district of Bercy and the Palais Omnisports, and close to the historical area of the Marais and the numerous town houses. We can cross over to the left bank of the Seine to stroll around the Jardin des Plantes, before going to the buzzing and festive quarter of Bastille for the night. For a business trip or a simple visit, the Grand Hôtel is a refined getaway for an original stay.
http://www.grand-hotel-dore.com/paris/
